ggplot(kind)+
  geom_bar(mapping = aes(x = `점유형태`,
                         y = `per`), stat = "identity", position = "dodge",
           fill = c("red",rep("yellowgreen",5)),col ="black")+theme_bw()+
  geom_text(mapping = aes(x=`점유형태`,
                          y=`per`+1,
                          label= `per`))+theme_void()+
  geom_text(mapping = aes(x=`점유형태`,
                          y=-2,
                          label = `점유형태`), size = 4.5)
